:INFO
Growth Tactics for Local News Newsletters
Specific strategies that work for growing a paid local journalism newsletter beyond the initial audience of friends and neighbors.

:TASK
[ ] Post a teaser of each story in local Facebook groups with a link
[ ] Ask every source you interview to share the story with their network
[ ] Set up a referral program with Substack Recommendations
[ ] Comment thoughtfully on local subreddits and link when relevant
[ ] Partner with a local radio station for a weekly 3-minute segment
[ ] Attend city council meetings and introduce yourself publicly
[ ] Run a free trial month once per quarter to capture fence-sitters
[ ] Email lapsed subscribers with a single free story as a reengagement

:NOTE
Word of mouth from civic leaders and local business owners is the highest-leverage growth channel for local news. Prioritize relationships with people who have large local networks.
